snippet.title: Friday Night Funkin' Traumatizing Web Tales | Soup.Avi, Mickey Mouse, Shed.Mov, etc (FNF Mod/Horror)
snippet.description:
Friday Night Funkin' VS Traumatizing Web Tales | VS Soup.Avi, Mickey Mouse, MLP Shed.mov, Sad Mouse, Candle cove, Obey the Walrus and Poochee and Pansy in 2160p Ultra HD.
Traumatizing Web-Tales Official Channel: https://youtu.be/Q6mCySf4ZXc

This is a mod based on scary web tales from the early days of the internet posted on internet forums or through scary videos, in this mod, Boyfriend and Pico will rap battle against our childhood nightmares such as RayRay from soup.Avi, Mickey Mouse, MLP Shed.mov, Sad Mouse, Candle Cove, Obey the Walrus, Poochee and Pansy. This is my playthrough of the Traumatizing Web Tales Mod.

FNF Trauma | Traumatizing Web Tales Mod Download
https://gamebanana.com/mods/489723

Game Note: A mod about childhood trauma/internet horror from the web/youtube videos/etc.
Relive YOUR Nightmares... Are you Nostalgic for Internet horror? 

Reminder: This isn't Thursday Night Trauma mod

All Web Tales References / Creepypasta:
1) Shed.mov
https://youtu.be/cH-yA8U2XgI
https://ponymov.fandom.com/wiki/SHED.MOV?mobile-app=true&theme=dark
2) Soup.avi | Blank Room Soup
https://youtu.be/6VMRAGxjOoA
https://creepypasta-land.fandom.com/wiki/Blank_Room_Soup
3) Sad Mouse
https://youtu.be/i7084dPvJjA
https://creepypastafiles.fandom.com/wiki/Suicide_Mouse
4) Candle Cove
https://youtu.be/bSaJEUB9oMw
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Candle_Cove
5) You are an idiot (website)
A computer virus that creates, like, infinity browser tabs to annihilate your RAM
https://youtu.be/JBzyvJHhJQ4
6) Obey the Walrus
https://youtu.be/FHviwdECNjU
https://creepy-videos.fandom.com/wiki/Obey_The_Walrus
7) Poochee and Pansy - Part 1: The Quest for the Midnight Crown (Remastered)
https://youtu.be/LiMvx_MtW5o
https://creepy-videos.fandom.com/wiki/Poochee_and_Pansy
